---
description: Keep handwritten C# files small and split by responsibility
globs: **/*.cs
alwaysApply: false
---

# File Size Limit

- Handwritten C# source files should stay at or below `200` total lines.
- If a change would push a file beyond `200` lines, extract a helper, mapper, validator, options type, endpoint handler, or domain/application/infrastructure collaborator into its own file.
- Keep one clear responsibility per file; do not keep unrelated helpers together just to avoid creating a new file.
- Generated files may exceed this limit when the generator controls the shape, such as EF Core migration designer files or model snapshots.
